  "properties": {
    "n_tokens": 49,
    "description": "Winner-take-all output area. All output nodes feed into the inhibitor (0.3); the inhibitor suppresses all output nodes via strong negative spatial edges (-0.5). The most strongly driven output node overcomes the inhibition and wins the competition. Its token IS the output. Strong inhibition is critical: without it, non-target outputs develop positive error during training, strengthening echo edges (digit→same digit) that cause succession degradation."
  }
